main event: A witness observed a bright red, round object resembling the size of a penny at an elevation of 15 degrees in the northwest, using binoculars.
interesting points: The object was observed for at least 1 1/2 hours before the report was made., The sighting occurred on Samish Island, Washington., The duration of the sighting coincided with the position of Venus in the sky., There were no photographs included with the report., Similar sightings were reported on previous dates by other witnesses.
